zogene Austauschgespräche mit Abgeordneten des Deutschen Bundestages, insbesondere während den Sitzungswochen, an und plant Anlass- und Einladungsbezogen als Gast an entsprechenden AG-, Arbeitskreis- und Ausschusssitzungen sowie an Fraktionsveranstaltungen teilzunehmen. \r\n","activityOperationType":"SELF_OPERATED","clientOrganizations":[],"clientPersons":[],"codexViolation":false,"disclosureRequirementsExist":false,"donationInformationRequired":false,"donators":[],"employeeCount":{"from":1,"to":10},"fieldsOfInterest":[{"code":"FOI_BUNDESTAG","de":"Bundestag","en":"Bundestag"},{"code":"FOI_BUNDESTAG|FOI_BUNDESTAG_PARLIAMENTARY","de":"Parlamentarisches Verfahren","en":"Parliamentary procedure"},{"code":"FOI_ECONOMY","de":"Wirtschaft","en":"Economy"},{"code":"FOI_ECONOMY|FOI_ECONOMY_HANDCRAFT","de":"Handwerk","en":"Handcraft"},{"code":"FOI_ECONOMY|FOI_ECONOMY_SAM_BUSINESS","de":"Kleine und mittlere Unternehmen","en":"Small and medium business"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING","de":"Bildung und Erziehung","en":"Education and parenting"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_ACADEMIC","de":"Hochschulbildung","en":"Academic education"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_CHILDHOOD","de":"Vorschulische Bildung","en":"Early childhood education"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_OTHER","de":"Sonstiges im Bereich „Bildung und Erziehung“","en":"Other in the field of “Education and parenting”"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_SCHOOL","de":"Schulische Bildung","en":"School education"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_WORK","de":"Berufliche Bildung","en":"Job education"},{"code":"FOI_HEALTH","de":"Gesundheit","en":"Health"},{"code":"FOI_HEALTH|FOI_HEALTH_CARE","de":"Pflege","en":"Health care"},{"code":"FOI_HEALTH|FOI_HEALTH_OTHER","de":"Sonstiges im Bereich „Gesundheit“","en":"Other in the field of “Health”"},{"code":"FOI_OTHER"},{"code":"FOI_POLITICAL_PARTIES","de":"Politisches Leben, Parteien","en":"Political life, parties"},{"code":"FOI_STATE_ADM